Recommends: code
Suggests: subversion
Description: HPE Server BIOS development tool
 BIOS Tool simplifies HPE Server BIOS development by providing:
  - Minimal setup with automatic worktree detection
  - Easy navigation in BIOS source trees  
  - Version control integration (Git/SVN)
  - Simple BUILD and CLEAN commands with intelligent output filtering
  - Build completion notifications
  - VS Code extension for integrated development
